msgid "maxframe.tensor.nanargmin"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanargmin.nanargmin:1 of
msgid ""
"Return the indices of the minimum values in the specified axis ignoring "
"NaNs. For all-NaN slices ``ValueError`` is raised. Warning: the results "
"cannot be trusted if a slice contains only NaNs and Infs."
msgstr ""
"返回指定轴上忽略 NaN 的最小值的索引。对于全为 NaN 的切片，会引发 ``"
"ValueError``。警告：如果切片只包含 NaN 和无穷大值，则结果不可信。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanargmin.nanargmin of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanargmin.nanargmin:5 of
msgid "Input data."
msgstr "输入数据。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanargmin.nanargmin:7 of
msgid "Axis along which to operate. By default flattened input is used."
msgstr "操作的轴。默认使用展平后的输入。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanargmin.nanargmin of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanargmin.nanargmin:10 of
msgid "**index_array** -- A tensor of indices or a single index value."
msgstr "**index_array** -- 索引的张量或单个索引值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanargmin.nanargmin of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanargmin.nanargmin:13 of
